name: Ukraine byviki
description:
I am from Ukraine 🇺🇦 I think we all know the situation. I left my home in Kyiv, my parent staying in another city in Ukraine where situation is not good . 
I made this art to help my country. 
You can buy it for the smallest price to share the information. And please donate my country how much u can 
We need your support.
You can do it here https://savelife.in.ua/donate/
Also u can go for a meeting in your country. 
Also, if you wanna help me u can write me. Maybe u can help me with house in Europe or food or send money on my wallet. Connect me in twitter please @byviki00
